OL,5, A black mother and four children, who  
OL,6, were held at gunpoint by police in     
OL,7, Colorado, have been awarded $1.9m      
OL,8, (#1.5m) in a settlement.               
OL,10,FBrittney Gilliam was wrongfully stopped
OL,11,Fin 2020 at a parking lot, along with   
OL,12,Fher six-year-old daughter, nieces aged 
OL,13,F14 and 17, and sister, 12.             
OL,15,FThe incident, which was caught on      
OL,16,Fcamera, drew outrage at the time.      
OL,18,FMs Gilliam later sued the officers     
OL,19,Faccusing them of "profound and         
OL,20,Fsystemic" racism.                      
